data.description: Cute one story 3 bed 2 bath ranch in quiet neighborhood with open living area and split bedroom floorplan in Rougemont.  Large over 1 acre lot with fenced in back yard perfect for pets and playing. Brand new HVAC system. Enjoy living in the country but still convenient to Durham and Roxboro. $2,500 flooring allowance with acceptable offer.
